title: [Brace Yourself]
description: A layer of debris extends from the entryway to a set of swinging doors in the back of this cramped space.  Several broken windows provide glimpses of the trees and water outside, and the incoming rays of moonlight highlight motes of dust falling from the sagging, low patchwork ceiling.  A motley assortment of rusty iron stands lean haphazardly against the grimy, limestone walls.
